  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    InputStrategy
    Defines a strategy for collecting input from the turn player to make a move.

    Sends a message to the Controller.

    Defines a strategy for displaying output to the user.

    A stream to send messages to display.

    Sends a message to start a new game to the Controller.

    A Reversi piece that is not empty.

    An icon that contains a Reversi piece.
    TileShell
    The shell of a tile, including the ability to click to place a piece there.

    The View for a Reversi game.
